%N A395461 Expansion of e.g.f. x^3*(1 + x + x^2/2 + x^3/6)*exp(x).
%C A395461 Number of words of length n defined on {a, b, c, d, e} that contain one a, one b, one c, at most three d's, and any number of e's.
%H A395461 <a href="/index/Rec#order_07">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (7,-21,35,-35,21,-7,1).
%F A395461 a(n) = n*(n-1)*(n-2)^2*(n^2-7*n+18)/6.
%F A395461 a(n) = 6*binomial(n,3)*Sum_{k=0..3} binomial(n-3,k).
%F A395461 G.f.: 6*x^3*(1 + x + 5*x^2 + 13*x^3)/(1 - x)^7. - _Stefano Spezia_, May 02 2026
%t A395461 a[n_]:= n*(n-1)*(n-2)^2*(n^2-7*n+18)/6; Array[a,36,0] (* _Stefano Spezia_, May 02 2026 *)
